      <div class="msgContentFrame">I think Damnation has naturally lower acc due to its power. I mean to balance the fact that Scourge or Banish deal between 1/3 to 1/2 its damage, yet they have a cast time and mp cost, while Damnation is free after using minimal darts to load TP, and gives back some MP. I mean if your stats are allocated similar to mine, then your Scourge/Banish is probably hitting and sticking 80% or greater on greens, where as Damnation is 50% to 66% or so. I think this is what will keep us Thaums from just using darts and Damnation when grouping against strong stuff... meaning its about balance and they want us to cast, but think about MP. Plus, dex clearly states physical and piety magical, and nowhere in Damnation's description states anything is physical. My theory at least and could be wrong.  <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Sep 15th 2010 10:58pm by Toryu </span></i></div>
